== 环保评级 ==
2018年12月，[[世界自然基金会|世界自然基金会]]（WWF）发布官方报告，包含对瑞士15个主要钟表及珠宝生产商的环保评级。<ref name=":442">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wwf.ch/sites/default/files/doc-2018-12/2018_12_07_WWF%20Watch%20and%20Jewellery%20Report%202018_final_e_0.pdf|title=Environmental rating and industry report 2018|last=|first=|date=|website=World Wide Fund for Nature|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120043234/https://www.wwf.ch/sites/default/files/doc-2018-12/2018_12_07_WWF%20Watch%20and%20Jewellery%20Report%202018_final_e_0.pdf|archive-date=2019-01-20|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-01-19}}</ref><ref name=":45">{{Cite web|url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/politics/benchmark-report_swiss-luxury-watches-fail-to-meet-environmental-standards/44628536|title=Swiss luxury watches fail to meet environmental standards|last=swissinfo.ch|first=S. W. I.|last2=Corporation|first2=a branch of the Swiss Broadcasting|website=SWI swissinfo.ch|language=en|access-date=2019-01-19|archive-date=2019-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120043225/https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/politics/benchmark-report_swiss-luxury-watches-fail-to-meet-environmental-standards/44628536|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其中万国表排名第一，获得高评分（“Ambitious”）。万国公司作为唯一一个获得“Ambitious”高评分的生产商，在报告中被评价为“认真坚持向可持续发展的转型，但同时还有极大的进步空间 （serious commitment towards a sustainable transformation, but with substantial potential for improvement）"。<ref name=":442" /><ref name=":443">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wwf.ch/sites/default/files/doc-2018-12/2018_12_07_WWF%20Watch%20and%20Jewellery%20Report%202018_final_e_0.pdf|title=Environmental rating and industry report 2018|last=|first=|date=|website=World Wide Fund for Nature|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120043234/https://www.wwf.ch/sites/default/files/doc-2018-12/2018_12_07_WWF%20Watch%20and%20Jewellery%20Report%202018_final_e_0.pdf|archive-date=2019-01-20|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-01-19}}</ref>

在钟表及珠宝制造行业，主要的环保隐患有二：1）生产活动的不透明；2）对珍贵原材料的大量开采，主要包括[[金|金矿]]。而后者是造成众多环境问题的重要因素之一，比如水土污染、土壤退化、森林破坏等。<ref name=":442" /><ref name=":45" /> 据估计，钟表及珠宝行业每年消耗超过2000吨的黄金，占全球黄金产量的50%以上，而大多数情况下，钟表制造公司不能或不愿意说明其原材料的来源以及原材料供应商是否采用环保的开采方式。<ref name=":442" /> 自21世纪初，万国公司就积极参与环境保护及[[可持续发展|可持续发展]]。<ref name=":12">{{Cite web|url=https://journal.hautehorlogerie.org/en/the-watch-industry-embraces-environmental-concerns/|title=The watch industry embraces environmental concerns – FHH Journal|website=journal.hautehorlogerie.org|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-21|archive-date=2019-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190218174818/https://journal.hautehorlogerie.org/en/the-watch-industry-embraces-environmental-concerns/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":02">{{Cite web|url=https://journal.hautehorlogerie.org/en/iwc-commits-to-transparency/|title=IWC commits to transparency – FHH Journal|website=journal.hautehorlogerie.org|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-21|archive-date=2019-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122045715/https://journal.hautehorlogerie.org/en/iwc-commits-to-transparency/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.iwc.com/gb/en/company/sustainability-at-iwc/our-environment.html|title=Environmental sustainability {{!}} IWC Schaffhausen|website=www.iwc.com|language=en-GB|access-date=2019-01-21|archive-date=2019-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122100124/https://www.iwc.com/gb/en/company/sustainability-at-iwc/our-environment.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2018年，万国公司更是坚持“透明”的经营原则，发布了瑞士奢侈钟表品牌的第一份基于Global Reporting Initiative (GRI) 所制定的“全球最佳生产标准（global best-practice standards）的可持续发展报告。<ref name=":02" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://press.iwc.com/iwc-sustainability-report-2018-en/|title=IWC LAUNCHES SUSTAINABILITY REPORTING IN ACCORDANCE WITH GRI STANDARDS|website=IWC LAUNCHES SUSTAINABILITY REPORTING IN ACCORDANCE WITH GRI STANDARDS|language=en|access-date=2019-01-21|archive-date=2019-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122044316/https://press.iwc.com/iwc-sustainability-report-2018-en/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

